<plot>A cold Moscow night. Two people, a white young man and a black young woman, are sitting in an empty train when three skinheads come and start harassing the girl. The young man comes to her rescue and gets beaten up. The girl takes him to her home. Few days later, he comes to see her again. She doesn't mind. He likes her, that leaves her indifferent. One night he comes to see her again only to understand that he is the only one who's playing the game of love.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?654683</url></doc>
